articles.title: Ferrari will have "private discussion" over Sainz F1 damage compensation - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Ferrari Formula 1 boss Fred Vasseur says he will talk to the stakeholders of the Las Vegas GP regarding compensation for the damage to Carlos Sainz's car in FP1.
articles.content:
Sainz ran over a metal water valve cover that had come loose and destroyed the chassis, power unit and energy store of his SF-23.
